### 2. System Message Rendering (11 action handlers)

Each `SystemActionType` has a dedicated handler that generates i18n keys + interpolation values:

| Action           | Handler File                           | Key Pattern                                                                                                            | Notes                                            |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| `CREATE_GROUP`   | ŌåÆ delegates to `add-members-action.ts` | `chat.system.add_members.*`                                                                                            | Shares logic with ADD_MEMBERS                    |
| `ADD_MEMBERS`    | `add-members-action.ts`                | `.single_self`, `.many_self`, `.many_self_count`, `.single_other`, `.many_other`, `.many_other_count`, `.joined_group` | Branches by: self/other, count Ōēż3/>3             |
| `REMOVE_MEMBER`  | `remove-member-action.ts`              | `.self_removed`, `.by_you`, `.by_actor`                                                                                | Shows target avatar                              |
| `LEAVE_GROUP`    | `leave-group-action.ts`                | `.self`, `.by_actor`                                                                                                   | ŌĆö                                                |
| `PROMOTE_ADMIN`  | `promote-admin-action.ts`              | `.self_promoted`, `.by_you`, `.by_actor`                                                                               | Renders `PromoteAdminCard` for the promoted user |
| `DEMOTE_ADMIN`   | `demote-admin-action.ts`               | `.self_demoted`, `.by_you`, `.by_actor`                                                                                | ŌĆö                                                |
| `TRANSFER_OWNER` | `transfer-owner-action.ts`             | `.self_promoted`, `.by_you`, `.by_actor`                                                                               | Renders `OwnerCard` for the new owner            |
| `UPDATE_NAME`    | `update-name-action.ts`                | `.update_name`                                                                                                         | Includes Pencil icon, shows oldName ŌåÆ newName    |
| `UPDATE_AVATAR`  | `update-avatar-action.ts`              | `.update_avatar`                                                                                                       | ŌĆö                                                |
| `DISBAND_GROUP`  | `disband-group-action.ts`              | `.disband_group`                                                                                                       | Includes Delete conversation button              |

**System message UI:** Displays target avatars, clickable names (opens OthersProfileDialog), delete button for DISBAND/REMOVE(self)/LEAVE(self). For PROMOTE_ADMIN and TRANSFER_OWNER, when the current user is the target, renders the notification card (PromoteAdminCard/OwnerCard) instead of the text bubble. For PROMOTE_ADMIN bubbles a green `Key` icon is shown; for DEMOTE_ADMIN a `Key+X` overlay icon is shown.

### 3. API Hooks (9 mutations + 3 queries)

**Mutations:**

| Hook                               | API                                        | Invalidation                                                                                                                                         |
| ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `useCreateGroupMutation`           | `POST /conversations/groups`               | conversations (prepends new group to top)                                                                                                            |
| `useAddMembersMutation`            | `POST /conversations/{id}/members`         | conversations, messages, friendsDirectory, search-members                                                                                            |
| `useRemoveMemberFromGroupMutation` | `DELETE /conversations/{id}/members/{uid}` | conversations, messages, group-members                                                                                                               |
| `usePromoteToAdminMutation`        | `PATCH /.../promote`                       | conversations, messages, group-members                                                                                                               |
| `useDemoteFromAdminMutation`       | `PATCH /.../demote`                        | conversations, messages, group-members                                                                                                               |
| `useUpdateGroupNameMutation`       | `PATCH /conversations/{id}/name`           | conversations                                                                                                                                        |
| `useUpdateGroupAvatarMutation`     | `PATCH /conversations/{id}/avatar`         | conversations (FormData multipart)                                                                                                                   |
| `useLeaveGroupMutation`            | `DELETE /conversations/{id}/leave`         | conversations (filtered out), messages (removed); passes optional `transferTo` for owner leave (transfer + leave handled atomically in one API call) |

**Queries:**

| Hook                       | Triggered When                  | Returns                           |
| -------------------------- | ------------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| `useFriendsDirectory`      | Dialog open + no search query   | Friends grouped A-Z (TreeMap)     |
| `useSearchMembersInfinite` | Query present (debounced 300ms) | Matching friends, paginated       |
| `useGroupMembersInfinite`  | Members tab open                | Members sorted by role, paginated |

### 4. WebSocket Real-time Updates

**Conversation cache updates on socket event:**

| Action Type                              | Behavior                                                                 |
| ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Normal messages, ADD_MEMBERS             | Move conversation to top, increment unreadCount                          |
| LEAVE_GROUP, REMOVE_MEMBER               | Do **not** move to top; only update lastMessage, remove member from list |
| DISBAND_GROUP, REMOVE(self), LEAVE(self) | Clear messages cache, conversation disabled                              |
| ADD_MEMBERS (self re-added)              | Invalidate messages cache ŌåÆ refetch (BE filters by joinedAt)             |

**Read receipts:** Updates `lastReadMessageId` in `conversation.members` for the specific user.

### 5. Role-Based UI

| Role       | Visible Actions                                                                                                              |
| ---------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **OWNER**  | All: Management tab (full), promote/demote, remove any member, disband, avatar/name edit                                     |
| **ADMIN**  | Management tab (restricted ŌĆö no owner/deputy section, no disband), remove Member-role only, avatar/name edit                 |
| **MEMBER** | Management tab locked (blur + ban icon overlay), can only view member list and leave group. No action menus on other members |

### 6. Leave / Disband UX Flows

**Leave Group (non-Owner):**

1. Click "Leave Group" in sidebar ŌåÆ `LeaveGroupDialog` opens
2. Toggle "Silent mode" (leave without sending notification)
3. Confirm ŌåÆ mutation fires ŌåÆ success toast ŌåÆ 900ms delay ŌåÆ conversation removed from list

**Leave Group (Owner ŌĆö Transfer Ownership Flow):**

1. Click "Leave Group" in sidebar ŌåÆ `TransferOwnerDialog` opens
2. Search/select a new group owner from the member list (radio buttons)
3. Click "Select and continue" ŌåÆ `LeaveGroupDialog` opens
4. Toggle "Silent mode" if desired, click "Leave group"
5. On confirm ŌåÆ single `leaveGroup` API call (with `transferTo` param) ŌåÆ BE handles transfer + leave atomically
6. Cancel at any step ŌåÆ no changes made (neither transfer nor leave happens)

**Disband Group (Owner only):**

1. Sidebar ŌåÆ Management tab ŌåÆ scroll to "Disband group"
2. Click ŌåÆ confirmation dialog
3. Confirm ŌåÆ `disbandGroupApi` ŌåÆ `isDisbanded=true`
4. Sidebar shows "Group has been disbanded" + Delete button
5. Input composer disabled, cannot send messages

### 7. Member Add/Search Flow

**Directory mode** (default when dialog opens):

- Shows all friends grouped alphabetically A-Z
- Existing group members shown as "Already joined" (disabled, checkmark icon)

**Search mode** (user types name or phone):

- Debounced 300ms, strips leading "+" (for phone numbers)
- Infinite scroll pagination
- Same `isAlreadyMember` disable logic

**Selected sidebar:** Shows selected members list, X button to deselect, badge counter.

