## How Has This Been Tested? (Manual)

1. Run FE Web locally (`npm run dev`).
2. Login with test accounts: Owner, Admin, Member.
3. Verify each flow:

| Test Case                                                                 | Expected                                                     | Checked |
| ------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------- |
| Create group from dialog: select Ōēź2 friends, set name, crop avatar        | Group created, redirected to group, IntroCard displayed      | [x]     |
| Directory A-Z shows correct order, existing members show "Already joined" | Grouped alphabetically, disabled for existing members        | [x]     |
| Search member by name + phone number                                      | Correct results, infinite scroll works                       | [x]     |
| Add member from group settings                                            | Member list updated, system message broadcast                | [x]     |
| Remove member (Owner/Admin click)                                         | Member removed from list, system message shown               | [x]     |
| Promote/Demote admin                                                      | Role badge updated, PromoteAdminCard shown for target        | [x]     |
| Leave group (public)                                                      | Toast ŌåÆ 900ms delay ŌåÆ conversation removed from list         | [x]     |
| Leave group (silent)                                                      | Only admins/owner see system message                         | [x]     |
| Disband group (Owner)                                                     | Confirmation ŌåÆ sidebar shows "disbanded" ŌåÆ input disabled    | [x]     |
| WebSocket: new message ŌåÆ conversation moves to top                        | Conversations list sorted correctly                          | [x]     |
| WebSocket: LEAVE/REMOVE ŌåÆ conversation stays in place                     | lastMessage updated but position unchanged                   | [x]     |
| Role-based: Member cannot see Management tab or action menus              | Only sees leave + view members                               | [x]     |
| Rename group: pre-fills current name, validates same name                 | Dialog shows current name selected, blocks save if unchanged | [x]     |
| Update avatar: crop ŌåÆ upload ŌåÆ new avatar displayed                       | Multipart file upload, avatar updated in real-time           | [x]     |

